									VI Editor

Command mode 
Insert mode  i
Execute mode  :wq  write and quit



Shift +I  :--- it will go in starting of line
- a  :- we can append data where cursor is there
Shift +A  :- it will go to end of current line
Small o :- it will create a new line where cursor is there
Shift o :- it will insert a new line before current line
Small s :- it will remove cursor pointing data
Dd - remove q entire line
2dd :- remove 2 line
Yy - copy a line
p---paste
